Installation Instructions,

First you will need Safari 5 (Mac or Windows) see,
http://www.apple.com/safari/

To install the Safari 5 Extension you have to “Enable the Develop menu” under the Advanced pane of Safari Preferences. 
Then from the Develop Menu you have to “Enable Extensions”.

Then you need to download the Netflix Queue Sorter.safariextz file from,
http://dl.dropbox.com/u/23267/NetflixQueueSorter.safariextz
Then double click on it to install it.


